data.description: Along 1604 your new home awaits!! Nestled on an 1/2 acre in the cul-de-sac of the Quiet Creek Subdivision, you'll find a stunning 1 story home with a spacious floor plan. This home features high ceilings, wooden beam accents, stainless steel appliances, and a kitchen meant for a chef. This home has 4 bedrooms 3 1/2 baths, and a 3 car tandem garage. The kitchen is a must see, with stainless steel gas cooktop, built-in oven and microwave, upgraded oversized granite island. Perfect home for entertaining with the open floor plan. A spacious primary bedroom with bay windows with views of the beautiful patio. The primary bathroom features a spa tub with dual vanities leading into the large walk-in closet. This home is accentuated with an enclosed tranquil sun room, where your busy day fades away and peace takes over. After relaxing in the costume designed sunroom, explore your large backyard with a custom deck, covered pergola and mature trees for additional relaxation and enjoyment.     Close to Ft. Sam, Randolph/SAMC, Forum.
